Package: FacileAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Analysis routines over a FacileDataStore
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steve", "Lianoglou", , "lianoglou@dnli.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Denali Therapeutics", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Provides modularized versions of analyses that are commonly
    performed over genomics data. The methods and API from the FacileViz package
    are used within to provide interactive htmlwidget-based vizualizations 
    for these results via the "vizualize" S3 generic.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    broom,
    checkmate,
    edgeR,
    FacileData,
    FacileViz,
    matrixStats,
    multiGSEA,
    plotly,
    tidyr
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat
License: Apache Version 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
